    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't trust them. my cousin took them and she said she felt like a zombie, like she wasn't even herself anymore. it feels like they just want to medicate the soul out of people so they're easier to manage. what if the \"help\" they offer is just a way to stop me from seeing things for what they really are? like, what if the sadness is actually the only real thing left?",
