    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. it feels like if i take those pills, i'm just lying to myself to survive a world that's broken. it feels like a trap. if the darkness is the only thing that's honest, then why am i supposed to fight it? i'm just so tired of fighting. is there even a way out that isn't just... pretending to be okay?",
